Sentencas: A single chamber solid oxide fuel cell (SC-SOFC) micro-stack with three series-wound cells has been prepared and operated in methane-oxygen-nitrogen mixture.
Titulo: Effects of the single chamber SOFC stack configuration on the performance of the single cells

Sentencas: A maximum power output of 282 mW was generated at the furnace temperature of 800 degrees C. A mutual effect was found among the three cells.
Titulo: Effects of the single chamber SOFC stack configuration on the performance of the single cells

Sentencas: Cell 2 between Cell 1 and Cell 3 produced a maximum power density of 215 mWcm(-2) which was higher than other cells.
Titulo: Effects of the single chamber SOFC stack configuration on the performance of the single cells

Sentencas: The heat effect and flow geometry were the main factors in inducing the difference among the three single cells.
Titulo: Effects of the single chamber SOFC stack configuration on the performance of the single cells
